ha visto duendes verdes.

107
00:08:52,120 --> 00:08:54,480
A ver si aprendemos a reconocer
una fuente fiable.

108
00:08:54,520 --> 00:08:55,600
Espérame arriba.

109
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:03,840
¿Esto de dónde lo has sacado,
Guzmán? -Ya te lo dije.

110
00:09:04,520 --> 00:09:06,080
